snippet.title: Metal Gear Solid Rising E3 2010 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Multi - platform Metal Gear featuring Raiden looks interesting.

This has since been canceled for a different version created by Platinum Games and published by Konami called Metal Gear Rising Revengeance.

Here is a brief summary, Metal Gear Solid Rising Revengeance is set in the near future where cyborg technology has become commonplace throughout society. As the world plunges further into asymmetric warfare, the only path that leads Raiden forward is rooted in resolving his past, and carving through anything that stands in his way.
